-- Mauritius’s Annual Inflation Rate Slows to 3.85% in March
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-04-06T05:59:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/mauritius-s-annual-inflation-rate-slows-to-3-85-in-march.html
Mauritius’s annual inflation slowed
to 3.85 percent in March compared with 4.1 percent in February,
Statistics Mauritius said.  Prices rose 0.3 percent during the month, the Port Louis-
based data agency said in a statement on its website today. The
inflation rate for the twelve months ended March 31 was 5.9%, it
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
